{"tid":1561432,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［膽小勿入］831.義士靈體疑似現身太子站","createTime":"2019-09-11T15:00:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T10:11:09.000Z","uid":109581,"like":2,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"c70dfe2bf3ad298da95e7b8d510e80024c66c7f8","tid":1561432,"uid":109581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:00:32.000Z","msg":"幫朋友代post...<br />\n<br />\n朋友行經太子地鐵站～ <br />\n為義士們送上一點心意⋯<br />\n心諗～<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">義士們⋯無人信你地的存在⋯<br />\n不如你地現身於鏡頭前⋯</span><br />\n所以⋯ <br />\n就拍下呢一張相⋯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XRuBMJ5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXRuBMJ5.jpg&h=f722ed13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知⋯⋯⋯<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">朋友真係影到義士⋯⋯</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冤有頭 債有主⋯<br />\n願831 的真相早日大白，<br />\n你們能沈冤得雪，還你地一個公道～！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FhtSj4D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFhtSj4D.jpg&h=66eac972&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXv1XRj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=h